Interpretation of a dream about gold by Ibn Sirin

preview.html: The interpretation of a dream about gold in a dream has many major differences between the majority of jurists and translators. There are those who said that it is an evil hidden from the viewer, and some confirmed that it is good, very blue, and an improvement. In romantic relationships, where the vision is interpreted according to what the viewer saw and according to the condition and quantity of the gold, we will tell you with all the indications for seeing gold through this article. Interpretation of a dream about gold Some jurists interpreted the dream about gold in general as undesirable, because the yellow color expresses problems and health problems, in addition To connotations and material losses. Ibn Shaheen says that collecting gold in a dream is a sign of the worries and problems that the dreamer carries, which cause him severe anxiety and psychological problems, especially if it is in its basic state without construction. Interpretation of a dream about gold by Ibn Sirin Ibn Sirin says that gold in a dream is In general, it is a bad thing and is a sign of a bad incident occurring to the dreamer, whether in the field of work or in the family environment. The dream of selling white gold, which Ibn Sirin says about, is an indication of the loss of something important in the dreamer’s life and may foretell the occurrence of a divorce or the loss of a job. Or children. Seeing a man wearing a golden bracelet, which Ibn Sirin says is an inheritance for a pioneer, or wearing a golden ring for a man means that he is suitable for the incompetent, and as a result he will suffer from many problems and instability in his marriage. Acquiring a gold bullion is evidence of the loss of money to the extent that it was affected in the dream. As for seeing the eye turned into gold, it is a bad vision that portends the loss of the dreamer’s sight. Dreaming that the walls of the house are plated with gold, which Ibn Sirin says about, is a vision that portends a fire in the dreamer’s house, and accordingly Be careful and take all precautions. Interpretation of a dream about gold for a single woman: Wearing a gold ring in a dream for an unmarried girl is considered a sign of a close relationship. As for the dream in which she is wearing a bicycle made of gold, it is undesirable and indicates that you will hear sad news or lose important things soon, which will cause her sadness and anxiety. Getting a gift of gold is an expression of a positive transformation in life and an indication of changes in many... Things that bring goodness and happiness. Seeing a gold chain in an unmarried woman’s dream is a sign of hearing good and promising news, in addition to stability, happiness, and compensation for the state of sadness she was going through, even if she was suffering from anxiety about something. Soon, God willing. What does buying gold in a dream mean for a single woman? Buying gold in a dream for an unmarried woman is a sign of stability in a romantic relationship or obtaining a job in a high position in society, and it can be an expression of engagement. As for buying a set of gold, it means Obtaining a large inheritance. As for buying a golden necklace, it is a sign of a new job, and the chain is a sign of achieving goals and ambitions. As for the vision of buying golden bracelets, it is a sign of freedom from judgments and problems in general, and Ibn Sirin says that it is a joy and a happy occasion that will happen to the girl, whether emotionally or practically. Interpretation of a dream about gold for a woman
